Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得两部魔神的光等人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续旅程寻找余下的一部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人被剑斗士拉法格袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但拉法格其实是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主的亲卫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被神官谢加图控制了的拉法格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为和光等人一战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而得回以前的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后更成为光等人的可靠战友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊诺巴的真面目和苏醒的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连晴天也不再了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被召唤到锡菲罗这里时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个美丽的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面裂开了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界真的开始崩溃了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿额上的宝石…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!又能见面了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近音讯断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怕是我和你们的最后通讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抑制着谢加图的石化魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来也已经到了极限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!振作点!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩溃的时刻正在逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 趁为时未晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海神瑟列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空神温达姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们闯过重重困难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功唤醒了两部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是余下最后一部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一部…魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 你们会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能实现艾美诺公主的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和锡菲罗一起崩溃和消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩溃!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会永远不能回到\N原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 异世界的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照莫歌拿的指示前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒最后一部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三部魔神…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫! 要消失了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 异世界的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的真正敌人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界…\N锡菲罗或许就有救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风 起程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…停手…\N这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会无法挽救…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主…艾美诺公主\N的情形怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始这场战争后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主的泪一直没停过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾、阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜、拉法格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全部都无法打倒魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…魔神!?\N这种力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你批准我再去讨伐魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我以这形态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经被那些异世界的少女击败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果能回复本来面目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能发挥所有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您答应我的请求!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下您一直把我留在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我是艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给殿下你的精兽!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你把我回复\N为这场战争开始前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在殿下\N你身边时的本来面目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊诺巴 你在精灵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有最强魔力的精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我能如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你变成人形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我曾经希望变成这样形态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想再次回复本来面目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我任性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以这形态 我能挥剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能负责监视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集回来打倒魔法骑士的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求殿下把我变成人形的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打倒成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及唤醒了两部魔神的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了用我的所有魔力战斗之外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别无他法!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊诺巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为我是公主送给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就长年累月把我留在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你现在\N再给我一次机会报恩!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变回精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能再次变回人形啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何不惜\N那样都要尽忠于我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直从旁看着公主和殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直留意着殿下你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个锡菲罗是意志的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心胜过一切的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下的心愿没理由不会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是从根本动摇锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的法规的邪恶心愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁想给你加上邪恶烙印也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下的意思就是世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 伊诺巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊诺巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野兽!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只野兽想杀死我们!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从异世界来的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?刚才脑海内…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那只\N白色野兽的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不可以再让你们前行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗那个美丽的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光 海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们平安地继续着旅程吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你保护从\N异世界唤来的三人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我送给这个人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非他偷来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时潜入城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从公主手中接过这通讯器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主为何知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时初次见面的我的名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小孩是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何呼唤我的名字!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊 魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还未知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你们在空之神殿见过面呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空之神殿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…\N当时那个…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫伊诺巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了谢加图殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉命前来消灭魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 对着恢复本来面目的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们输定了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…\N生下来就无亲无故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着孤独的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会再见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一的弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…\N艾美诺公主的…弟弟!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王姐 在分别之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你洗掉我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柱有支持这个世界的重要任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心有更少牵挂会比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不能再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免王姐你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会独自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请王姐你也忘记有我这个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从…你手上接过这个通讯器后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就离开了城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使洗掉记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你带着这个通讯器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了分开也能听到你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免忘记我最重要及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一一个弟弟的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才这么担心你的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道锡菲罗崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道你有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我唯一的王姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法…无效!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧 你的记忆也恢复了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王姐 你是王姐吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再次叫我做姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本应全部洗掉的记忆恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我的力量减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆的封印解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…帮不了王姐你吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有异世界的人才帮得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女们现在有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧\N请…请你帮助她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救魔法骑士!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作!风!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要设法对付那敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它下一次攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就会致我们于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你们支持到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要称赞你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那也到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光!海!风!听到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧 你平安无事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事不需挂心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听住 听清楚!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们正在交手的伊诺巴的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是额头上的饰物!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击那里!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑和魔法从刚才起完全无效!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想一个人冲过去!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经向很多人许下承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为魔法骑士 挽救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 努力吧 小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧!魔法骑士!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊诺巴…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海和小风也…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 已经没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只野兽…\N伊诺巴也被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠…菲力欧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 把弱点告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是菲力欧你的通讯器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:21:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主的力量\N已经变得很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经只能透过这个魔法用具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向你们传话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 它应该由你们保管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救艾美诺公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有从异世界来的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光 海还有风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们救救公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挽救这个锡菲罗!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了打倒魔法骑士的好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你再给我\N爱尔希欧蕾一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你…谢加图大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:38.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:45.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:51.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:58.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:03.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:10.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:16.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:23.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
